{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"58ee4177f9","title":"厕所闲谈","origin":"《重庆市右派言论选辑第二集》（内部文件，只供领导同志参考，请勿外传和翻印），中共重庆市委宣传部办公室编印，1957年8月。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"189a7e7e69","index":0,"year":1957,"month":5,"day":null,"articleId":"58ee4177f9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"3d6e05a0be","name":"重庆"},{"id":"4a71922736","name":"胥兴廉"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"64bb63e33e","type":"title","text":"厕所闲谈","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"7f5cf13824","type":"authors","text":"重庆胥兴廉","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"78a214e300","type":"paragraph","text":"[编者按：胥兴廉，男，37岁，地主家庭出身，现在西南纺管局工作。解放前曾参加三青团、国民党，参加过“中国民主自由社会主义学会”，并担任这个反动组织的机关刊物“主流”西南版总经理，大肆宣传反共，搞第三条路线。解放后，肃反中盗窃国家机密，散布反动言论，曾被斗争，因而心怀不满。此次借“鸣、放”机会否认自己的罪恶活动，说肃反100％的错了，并“写诗、著文”污蔑整风运动和党的各项政策。]","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"c615ee0858","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：为什么很多非党干部老不升级，少数党员干部年年高升，有的三年升四级？","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"3fb08536b7","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：一般偏低。重点突出，是我局干部工资政策！","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"b23b9fc3b7","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：陈静翰缺德鲜才不平八级工程师就不革命，结果如愿以偿，为什么？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"f86bfe5a34","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：人家是“特殊材料制成的！”","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"580216392e","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：为什么一般非党干部有缺点，常常大会批评，甚至斗争，党员干部犯了天大错亦无声无息？","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"209ce57ad5","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：“家丑不可外扬”！","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"d441266b5b","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：在肃反中代头打人的大批打手，都被提拔，试问他们有何德，何能呢？","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"dc44a7e9df","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：“党性很强，觉悟很高”武松会打真虎，他们会打假老虎，真真假假何必认真，然后革命。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"3fa1494199","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：为什么平常肯大胆提意见的人，大都成为肃反斗争的对象？","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"dadf8c5917","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：不服从领导就是反对党的领导，亦就是“反革命”，不斗一下，今后更不好领导。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"96fc53da2d","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：岂不怕冤枉好人，违反中央的政策？","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"6568700a9e","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：群众运动出点偏差，是不可避免的，颁发政策是在中央，掌握灵活性还在我们。","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"2acee82a92","type":"paragraph","text":"甲：你的马列主义真高，但我总觉得不对劲？","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"e0b6dd3301","type":"paragraph","text":"乙：这是我从革命实践中，创造性的发挥，但只能在厕所内闲谈。","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"87efc277b7","type":"subtitle","text":"整风有感（词）","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"ff596e1a5a","type":"paragraph","text":"整风运动何时了？   　“三害”知多少？","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"1d5062cbc7","type":"paragraph","text":"纺织大楼又东风；　　墙报不堪入目满局中。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"9501ebe7fb","type":"paragraph","text":"“积极分子”今犹在只是态度改；问君还有几多愁？恰似一江春水向东流。","index":20,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"653e203864","type":"subtitle","text":"前题  　七言一首","index":21,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"0c24d188d5","type":"paragraph","text":"八面威风一旦扫？  领导工作如何搞？","index":22,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"58ee4177f9"},{"id":"48ffa5cb95","type":"paragraph","text":"众怒难犯势汹汹，满局风雨何时收，","index":23,